The test checks that the method throws an IllegalArgumentException if an empty parameter's List is passed
The test checks that the method throws an IllegalArgumentException if zero was passed as a parameter
The test checks that the method throws an IllegalArgumentException if not enough parameters are passed for this shape
The test checks that the method throws an IllegalArgumentException if too many parameters are passed for this shape
The test checks that the method throws an IllegalArgumentException if one of the parameters is a negative number
